<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="C" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Christmas" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Christmas,</orth> the festival celebrated in memory of the birth of Christ: <cit><quote>at C.</quote> <bibl n="shak. lll 1.1.105" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL I, 1, 105</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>to dash it like a C. comedy,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lll 5.2.462" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 2, 462</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>a C. gambold or a tumbling-trick,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lll 5.2.140" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. Ind. 2, 140.</bibl></cit>
